sql_json.natural_language: Who did we email most recently this week?
sql_json.generated_sql: SELECT toPeople, toEmails, sentAt, snippet, messageId, threadId FROM email_search_index WHERE sentAt >= TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 7 DAY) ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1;
